  "question": "A premenopausal 44-year-old woman under-goes a quadrantectomy and node dissection for a 2-cm infiltrating carcinoma of the left breast. The margins are clear, and 5 out of 15 lymph nodes are involved. ER and PR are positive. Recommended adjuvant therapy should include which of the following?",
