  "question": "A45-year-old premenopausal woman undergoes a left breast lumpectomy for a 1.5-cm, lymph node positive, hormone sensitive invasive breast cancer. She receives chemotherapy, radiotherapy, and is on tamoxifen. Recommended follow-up after therapy should always include:",
