  "id": 130143,
  "question": "A25-year-old nonalcoholic man has noticeable right gynecomastia since age 20. He is most uncomfortable and reluctant to swim or exer-cise at a gym for fear of being an object of deri-sion. He should be advised to have which of the following?",
