  "id": 130144,
  "question": "A36-year-old woman presents with a substantial unilateral breast enlargement. She had presumed that this was normal, but on examination, a large, firm tumor is palpated by the attending physi-cian. There is early erosion on the skin. Afavor-able outlook can be anticipated if the lesion is which of the following?",
