  "question": "A 64-year-old man complains of pain in the lower chest. ACT scan confirms the presence of a tumor of the lung at T10 level to the left of the midline and invading the surrounding left lung base. Because of the structure most likely involved and penetrating the diaphragm at this level, what could be associated?",
