  "question": "A30-year-old executive learns that he has a duo-denal ulcer. His gastroenterologist prescribes and outlines medical therapy. The patient worries that if medical therapy fails he may need surgery. Which of the following is the best indication for elective surgical therapy for duodenal ulcer disease?",
