  "question": "Investigations of a 43-year-old woman with pluriglandular syndrome were scheduled to determine if a gastrinoma (ZES) was present. The serum gastrin level was slightly elevated. Further assessment to establish the diagnosis can be made by repeating the serum gastrin level after stimulation with which of the following?",
