  "id": 130572,
  "question": "A 62-year-old male presents with an irreducible swelling and severe pain in the left groin. He had a known reducible hernia for 15 years prior to this. He had a bowel movement while in the emergency room. At surgery, a Richter’s hernia was found. Which of the following statements is TRUE?",
