  "question": "A 55-year-old woman, who recently had been dieting with a weight loss of 20 lb, presents with a small-bowel obstruction and pain, which radiates down the inside of her thigh to the knee. She has no past history of abdominal surgery. Which of the following is the likely diagnosis?",
