  "question": "A 38-year-old woman underwent an open cholecystectomy a week ago. She is found to have a subhepatic abscess and bacteremia. The preliminary blood culture report states that the organism cultured is an aerobic gram-negative rod. Of the antibiotics listed below, which would be the best choice?",
